   - Is it possible to set the `classifyOut-&gt;actionType` immediately and return this value before allocating any memory to copy the data into my queue. I assume this would prevent the slow down from happening?
  - What else should I be doing differently to prevent this?
 - If not,
   - What is causing the issue with the slow down here?

